# Go UHC - NHL Web Application (Refactored)

This is a Go-based web application that provides real-time NHL data for the Utah Hockey Club (Mammoth). The application serves as a comprehensive dashboard with live scoreboards, news, schedules, and team analysis.

## Modular Project Structure

### Main Entry Point
- **[main.go](mdc:main.go)** - Main application entry point with initialization and background processes

### Models (Data Structures)
- **[models/schedule.go](mdc:models/schedule.go)** - Schedule, Game, Broadcast, Team structs
- **[models/scoreboard.go](mdc:models/scoreboard.go)** - Scoreboard, ScoreboardGame, ScoreboardTeam structs  
- **[models/standings.go](mdc:models/standings.go)** - Standings, TeamStanding, TeamNameInfo structs
- **[models/news.go](mdc:models/news.go)** - NewsHeadline struct
- **[models/season.go](mdc:models/season.go)** - SeasonStatus struct
- **[models/performance.go](mdc:models/performance.go)** - TeamPerformance struct

### Services (Business Logic)
- **[services/nhl_api.go](mdc:services/nhl_api.go)** - NHL API integration and data fetching
- **[services/news_scraper.go](mdc:services/news_scraper.go)** - NHL news scraping functionality
- **[services/performance.go](mdc:services/performance.go)** - Team performance analysis
- **[services/season.go](mdc:services/season.go)** - Season detection and validation

### HTTP Handlers
- **[handlers/handlers.go](mdc:handlers/handlers.go)** - Handler initialization and shared state
- **[handlers/home.go](mdc:handlers/home.go)** - Main dashboard page with complete HTML template
- **[handlers/schedule.go](mdc:handlers/schedule.go)** - Schedule, banner, and upcoming games handlers
- **[handlers/news.go](mdc:handlers/news.go)** - News content handler
- **[handlers/scoreboard.go](mdc:handlers/scoreboard.go)** - Live scoreboard handler  
- **[handlers/analysis.go](mdc:handlers/analysis.go)** - Team analysis and season status handlers

